 Thompson for Congress]\n*{{Dmoz|Regional/North_America/United_States/Mississippi/Government/Federal/US_House_of_Representatives/Bennie_G._Thompson_%5BD-2%5D}}\n*{{CongLinks | congbio = t000193 | ballot = Bennie_Thompson | nndb = 707/000040587 | votesmart = 26929 | govtrack = 400402 | opencong = 400402 | rollcall = 280 | politifact = | ontheissues = House/Bennie_Thompson.htm | congress = bennie-thompson/1151 | worldcat = | fec = H4MS02068 | opensecrets = N00003288 | assets = bennie-thompson | legistorm = 504/Rep_Bennie_G_Thompson.html | followthemoney = | cspan = 7304 | imdb = | bloomberg = | nyt = | washpo = gIQAfwiAAP }}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-par|us-hs}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Mike Espy]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Member of the [[List of United States Representatives from Mississippi|U.S. House of Representatives]]<br>from [[Mississippi's 2nd congressional district]]|years=1993\u2013present}}\n{{s-inc}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Peter T. King|Peter King]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=Chairperson of the [[United States House Committee on Homeland Security|House Homeland Security Committee]]|years=2007\u20132011}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Peter T. King|Peter King]]}}\n|-\n{{s-prec|usa}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Nydia Vel\u00e1zquez]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[List of current members of the United States House of Representatives by seniority|United States Representatives by seniority]]|years=67th}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Sam Farr]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{MS-FedRep}}\n{{Authority control|VIAF=121196443}}\n\n{{Persondata <!-- Metadata: see [[Wikipedia:Persondata]]. -->\n| NAME              =Thompson, Bennie\n| ALTERNATIVE NAMES =\n| SHORT DESCRIPTION = American politician\n| DATE OF BIRTH     =1948-01-28\n| PLACE OF BIRTH    =[[Bolton, Mississippi]]\n| DATE OF DEATH     =\n| PLACE OF DEATH    =\n}}\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Thompson, Bennie}}\n[[Category:1948 births]]\n[[Category:African-American mayors]]\n[[Category:African-American members of the United States House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:African-American politicians]]\n[[Category: